{"tha-ap112:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap112:0.2":"Bhikkhadayivagga ","tha-ap112:0.3":"Renupujakattheraapadana ","tha-ap112:1.1":"“Suvannavannam sambuddham, ","tha-ap112:1.2":"Sataramsimva bhanumam; ","tha-ap112:1.3":"Obhasentam disa sabba, ","tha-ap112:1.4":"Ulurajamva puritam. ","tha-ap112:2.1":"Purakkhatam savakehi, ","tha-ap112:2.2":"sagareheva medanim; ","tha-ap112:2.3":"Nagam paggayha renuhi, ","tha-ap112:2.4":"vipassissabhiropayim. ","tha-ap112:3.1":"Ekanavutito kappe, ","tha-ap112:3.2":"yam renumabhiropayim; ","tha-ap112:3.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap112:3.4":"buddhapujayidam phalam. ","tha-ap112:4.1":"Pannatalisito kappe, ","tha-ap112:4.2":"renu namasi khattiyo; ","tha-ap112:4.3":"Sattaratanasampanno, ","tha-ap112:4.4":"cakkavatti mahabbalo. ","tha-ap112:5.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap112:5.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap112:5.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap112:6.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma renupujako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap112:7.1":"Renupujakattherassapadanam dasamam. ","tha-ap112:8.1":"Bhikkhadayivaggo ekadasamo. ","tha-ap112:9.1":"Tassuddanam ","tha-ap112:10.1":"Bhikkhadayi nanasanni, ","tha-ap112:10.2":"hatthiyo padapujako; ","tha-ap112:10.3":"Mutthipupphi udakado, ","tha-ap112:10.4":"nalamali upatthako; ","tha-ap112:10.5":"Bilalidayi renu ca, ","tha-ap112:10.6":"gathayo cha ca satthi ca. "}